**Story**
Saint Peter was hungry and faint with hunger . 
He reached the house of an old woman and asked him for one of her cakes ,
but the old woman refused to give him any cakes.
For her greed and selfishness , Saint Peter turned the old woman into a woodpecker which bores and bores
and bores to get her food.
Now the old woman had lost her food , fire and shelter only because of her selfishness and greed